Insert into KSLO_RICH_TEXT_T (FORMATTED,ID,OBJ_ID,PLAIN,VER_NBR) values ('THE OUTCOME OF THIS COURSE will include a refinement through practice of diction, syntax, line, stanza, figurative logic, argument (or plot), and sustained interplay of sound & meaning. You should be able to identify more accurately and more quickly these elements in poetry, and perceive how poets deploy them, and to what effect--in your own work, in the work of your colleagues, in the published work we read as a class, in the literary works you read in other classes, and on your own.','87aba195-1142-4ff8-be73-712cb5e68759','ab1e10ba-966f-409a-bf3f-d848079eecb7','THE OUTCOME OF THIS COURSE will include a refinement through practice of diction, syntax, line, stanza, figurative logic, argument (or plot), and sustained interplay of sound & meaning. You should be able to identify more accurately and more quickly these elements in poetry, and perceive how poets deploy them, and to what effect--in your own work, in the work of your colleagues, in the published work we read as a class, in the literary works you read in other classes, and on your own.',0)
