Insert into KSLO_RICH_TEXT_T (FORMATTED,ID,OBJ_ID,PLAIN,VER_NBR) values ('You should be able to identify more accurately and more quickly these elements in fiction, and perceive how writers deploy them, and to what effect--in your own work, in the work of your colleagues, in the published work we read as a class, and in the literary works you read in other classes, and on your own.','04886f02-3f06-4b5c-8b78-7a33374a3d3d','cbd599b6-877e-4339-8f09-fd567c5dcfb7','You should be able to identify more accurately and more quickly these elements in fiction, and perceive how writers deploy them, and to what effect--in your own work, in the work of your colleagues, in the published work we read as a class, and in the literary works you read in other classes, and on your own.',0)
