Insert into KSLO_RICH_TEXT_T (FORMATTED,ID,OBJ_ID,PLAIN,VER_NBR) values ('1)	Students will demonstrate systematic and analytical comprehension of European violence and Justice in the Old Regime and after. This will be accomplished through developing reading and writing skills in discussion, assignments, and exams. ','2c471106-0440-4c2b-8fc1-aa773e17fe86','1ce4390c-bc99-4746-8e79-997910edb97b','1)	Students will demonstrate systematic and analytical comprehension of European violence and Justice in the Old Regime and after. This will be accomplished through developing reading and writing skills in discussion, assignments, and exams. ',0)
/
Insert into KSLO_RICH_TEXT_T (FORMATTED,ID,OBJ_ID,PLAIN,VER_NBR) values ('2)	At the end of the course, students will appreciate how a society very different than our own nonetheless managed to endure for centuries without massive coercion. This will be a major theme of the seminars.','ec8b8618-973e-4bac-bf59-e088c68a4790','6f423283-acc8-4cf0-bf43-c89296dc2fb2','2)	At the end of the course, students will appreciate how a society very different than our own nonetheless managed to endure for centuries without massive coercion. This will be a major theme of the seminars.',0)
/
Insert into KSLO_RICH_TEXT_T (FORMATTED,ID,OBJ_ID,PLAIN,VER_NBR) values ('3)	Students will develop an understanding of the major theorists if justice during and after the period, for example, Beccaria and Foucault.','7a4de58f-3596-467e-97af-c5f678477c06','c11b4c0e-7397-460a-b89e-78b8ab9e83a4','3)	Students will develop an understanding of the major theorists if justice during and after the period, for example, Beccaria and Foucault.',0)
